) AS `t`

SELECT `o`.`Id`, `o`.`AccountId`, `o`.`Address`, `o`.`ContactDetails`, `o`.`CreatedAt`, `o`.`Email`, `o`.`TotalAmount`, `t`.`Id`, `t`.`BookId`, `t`.`OrderId`, `t`.`OrderPrice`, `t`.`Quantity`, `t`.`SubscriptionId`, `t`.`Id0`, `t`.`BookDate`, `t`.`BookDescription`, `t`.`BookImage`, `t`.`BookName`, `t`.`Price`, `t`.`Id1`, `t`.`SubDescription`, `t`.`SubPrice`, `t`.`SubType`

    LEFT JOIN `Books` AS `b` ON `o0`.`BookId` = `b`.`Id`
    LEFT JOIN `Subscriptions` AS `s` ON `o0`.`SubscriptionId` = `s`.`Id`
) AS `t0` ON `t`.`Id` = `t0`.`OrderId`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Id0`, `t0`.`Id`, `t0`.`Id0`
